所有硬币的正面图案为总统[[乔治·华盛顿|乔治·华盛顿]]的肖像，但其肖像将会重新设计。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Mike Unser |title=CCAC to Review First of the American Women Quarter Designs |url=https://www.coinnews.net/2021/04/02/ccac-to-review-first-of-the-american-women-quarter-designs/ |accessdate=2021-04-17 |publisher=CoinNews |date=2021-04-02}}</ref>[[美國美術委員會|美國美術委員會]]和{{le|公民造币咨询委员会|Citizens Coinage Advisory Committee}}目前建议采用由{{le|劳拉·加丁·弗雷泽|Laura Gardin Fraser}}于1931年设计的华盛顿肖像作为正面图案。弗雷泽的设计同时也是1999年{{le|半鹰金币|Half eagle}}的正面图案。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Paul Gilkes |title=Fraser portrait to finally debut on quarter in 2022 |url=https://www.coinworld.com/news/us-coins/fraser-portrait-to-finally-debut-on-quarter-in-2022 |accessdate=2021-04-26 |work=Coin World |date=2021-04-23}}</ref>

每枚硬币的背面都将纪念一名杰出美国女性。被选的女性需在[[美国妇女选举权|选举权]]、[[非裔美国人民权运动|民权]]、废奴、政府、人文、科学、太空、或艺术等领域中对美国作出重要的贡献。<ref name="bill" />受到表彰的女性将来自不同的种族和地域背景。该计划的授权法案要求硬币背面的设计不得包含任何在世的女性。<ref name="numismatic news">{{cite news |title=Mint Announces First Two American Women Quarter Honorees |url=https://www.numismaticnews.net/us-coins/mint-announces-first-two-american-women-quarter-honorees |accessdate=2021-04-21 |work=Numismatic News |date=2021-04-13}}</ref>[[美国财政部长|美国财政部长]][[珍妮特·耶伦|珍妮特·耶伦]]将征询公众的建议，并与[[史密森尼学会|史密森尼学会]]、{{le|国家女性历史博物馆|National Women's History Museum}}、和{{le|国会女性事务党团|Congressional Caucus for Women's Issues}}协商后最终决定该计划的获选女性名单。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Ellen Gutoskey |title=Which Trailblazing Women Should Be Featured on Quarters? The U.S. Mint Wants Your Suggestions |url=https://www.mentalfloss.com/article/645655/us-mint-women-collectible-quarters |accessdate=2021-04-21 |work=Mental Floss |date=2021-04-16}}</ref>

== 发行 ==
在计划的四年期间，美国铸币局每年将最多发行五种背面设计，总共最多发行二十种背面设计。<ref name="coinweek">{{cite news |author1=Louis Golino |title=The Coin Analyst: Have Circulating Commemorative Programs Outlasted Their Welcome? |url=https://coinweek.com/modern-coins/the-coin-analyst-have-circulating-commemorative-programs-outlasted-their-welcome/ |accessdate=2021-04-19 |publisher=CoinWeek |date=2021-01-28}}</ref>[[马娅·安杰卢|马娅·安杰卢]]、[[萨莉·莱德|萨莉·莱德]]、{{tsl|en|Wilma Mankiller|威尔马·曼基勒}}、{{tsl|en|Adelina Otero-Warren|阿德琳娜·奥特罗-沃伦}}和[[黄柳霜|黄柳霜]]将是2022年25美分硬币纪念的五位杰出美国女性。<ref name="numismatic news" /><ref>{{cite news |title=United States Mint Announces Additional Honorees In American Women Quarters™ Program |url=https://www.usmint.gov/news/press-releases/mint-announces-additional-honorees-in-american-women-quarters-program |accessdate=2021-06-13 |publisher=[[美国铸币局|美国铸币局]] |date=2021-06-09}}</ref>

== 反响 ==
许多钱币收藏家认为以美国杰出女性为题材的硬币系列应该由纪念币模式发行。有收藏家对重新设计其他面额的硬币并降低新硬币的发行频率更为感兴趣。<ref name="coinweek" />

